1:first its necessary to find out correct hostname
	it can be done using command $hostname
2:Hostname to IP address is done using 
	getaddrinfo
3:Four threads are used
4:2 lists, and 1 mutex and condition for each list
	i.e. for sending one list; and for recieveing on list
5: to install libcurses
	sudo apt install libncurses-dev
6: to run 
./s-talk 6001 $hostname 6000
./s-talk 6000 $hostname 6001
 	as i was running both on same system
 
